title: RHONJ: Shore-y, Not Shore-y — Live from Kansas!
description:
It's another day at the Jersey Shore on The Real Housewives of New Jersey, but this one ends with quite the twist, courtesy of Danielle Staub. We're recapping it all live from Lawrence F**kin' Kansas!!
